<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/guidelines.css">
    <title>Guidelines - <%= siteTitle %></title>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
    <main>
        <div class="guidelines__content">
            <h1 class="guidelines__content-title">Guidelines</h1>
            <div class="guidelines__content--1">
                <h2 class="guidelines__content-title-2">a) The following content will be posted unmodified:</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Actual confession</li>
                    <li>Wholesome and/or funny posts</li>
                    <li>Constructive criticism, neutral complains</li>
                    <li>Verified news</li>
                    <li>Events, request for help, questions, advertisements, job postings</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="guidelines__content--2">
                <h2 class="guidelines__content-title-2">b) The following content will be censored or labeled:</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Name calling in neutral/negative posts (e.g. Akari will be censored to A***i)</li>
                    <li>Photo with human face, username, personal information, or any sensitive information</li>
                    <li>Post with unverified/fake news, these will be labeled with a ‚ùå sign with a warning message (To
                        be considered as genuine news, it has to be verifiable from mainstream news sources)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="guidelines__content--3">
                <h2 class="guidelines__content-title-2">c) The following content will not be posted:</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Hate speech (not to be confused with constructive criticism)</li>
                    <li>18+ media of any purposes</li>
                    <li>Copyrighted content (meme is fine as long as the consensus signals fair use)</li>
                    <li>Duplicate posts (only the oldest one will be posted, cut off period is approximately one month)
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    <script src="/js/partials/navbar.js"></script>
</body>

</html>